f_C(c) &= \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} f_A(a)f_B(c-a)\,da \\
&= \int_0^{60} \frac{1}{60} \cdot \frac{1}{60} \, da \\
&= \frac{1}{60} \cdot \frac{1}{60} \cdot 60 \\
&= \frac{1}{60}
\end{align*}
